  "description": "The Filofax Personal Malden organiser is made from soft full grain buffalo leather with a natural two tone colour. The Malden is a very laid-back organiser with a soft, casual construction and rustic stitching. The closure is a leather strap with a branded metal poppercap. The left inside cover features three vertical slip pockets and a vertical zipped pocket. The right inside cover has a vertical slip pocket, notepad pocket and a leather pen loop. The Personal Malden organiser contains a selection of cotton cream inserts and a 2026 week to view diary. The mechanism has 6 rings of 23mm to hold paper size 95mm x 171mm.",
